<tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Blast from the PAST: Albany style Hunt Down V 1.0</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><table width='99' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'><tr><td background='/swtcg/gfx/5star.gif'><img src='/lotr/gfx/trans.gif' width='1' height='19'></td></tr></table><font size=1>(4.94)</font> | <A HREF="/starwarsccg/decks/decks.php?reviews=35157">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/starwarsccg/main/mpage.php?member=495">Matt "MattSokol" Sokol</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/starwarsccg/main/mpage.php?member=495&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Old School Hunt Down played by the dudes from Albany, New york.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> September 15, 2005</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Objective (1)<br />
